ğŸ”‘ Outcome: Clean, secure, and usable survey data.

4ï¸âƒ£ ANALYZE â€” Identify Key Insights

The analysis uncovered two major findings:
ğŸš© Negative Predictor:
Employees who experienced a long, complicated hiring process were more likely to leave early.

â­ Positive Predictor:
Employees with a transparent and efficient evaluation + feedback process were more likely to stay long-term.

ğŸ”‘ Outcome: Concrete factors linked to satisfaction and retention.

5ï¸âƒ£ SHARE â€” Communicate Results Effectively
